channel.title: Benthic Photo Survey
channel.description: Benthic Photo Survey is an open source software tool for efficiently processing photo transect data.

item.title: BPS v1.0.1 Release
item.description:
BPS v1.0.1 is ready for use. See the installation section of this site for how to get started. Then check out the docs, either on this site or on ReadTheDocs.org.

Future “News” items will (hopefully) include BPS use cases and publications.
